1
command to add group: sudo addgroup <groupname>

2
command to add user to engineers group: sudo usermod -aG engineers sam, sudo usermod -aG engineers joe,  sudo usermod -aG engineers amy,  sudo usermod -aG engineers sara

3
command to creat the shared folder:mkdir groupfolder

4
command to change ownership of engineers share folder to engineer group: sudo chgrp -R engineers groupfolder
